snippet.title: Spitfire '40 (1985) - Commodore 64
snippet.description:
Simple flight simulator from Mirrorsoft, released in 1985. The Commodore 64-version suffers from a very low framerate.

I'm no expert at this game, and I played for about 10 minutes before giving up on it. I did shoot down a few huns, though! ;)

http://www.spillhistorie.no/
